<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .header {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .date {
            text-align: right;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .title {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .content {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="date">Date: {{date}}</div>
        <p><strong>To,</strong></p>
        <p>The Scholarship Committee / Selection Board,</p>
        <p><strong>{{scholarshipName}}</strong> Office.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="title">SUBJECT: COVER LETTER FOR SCHOLARSHIP APPLICATION</div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Respected Sir/Madam,</p>

        <p>I, <strong>{{fullName}}</strong>, a resident of <strong>{{address}}</strong>, am writing this letter to
            formally apply for the <strong>{{scholarshipName}}</strong>. I am currently pursuing
            <strong>{{course}}</strong> at <strong>{{institution}}</strong>.</p>

        <p>My academic performance has been consistent, with a percentage of <strong>{{percentage}}%</strong> in my
            previous qualification. My annual family income is <strong>Rs. {{annualIncome}}</strong>, and receiving this
            scholarship would significantly assist me in continuing my education without financial burden.</p>

        <p>I have attached all the necessary documents for your verification. I hope for your favorable consideration of
            my application.</p>

        <p>Thank you.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature">
        <p>Yours Sincerely,</p>
        <br><br>
        <p>__________________________</p>
        <p><strong>{{fullName}}</strong></p>
        <p>Ph: {{phoneNumber}} / Email: {{email}}</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>